SHAPEFILE_2_NUMERIC_TYPE_ATTRIBUTE_HANDLING "$(SHAPEFILE_IN_NUMERIC_TYPE_ATTRIBUTE_HANDLING_SHAPEFILE_2)"
#Note: Using the search envelope requires the shape index files (.sbnand.sbx)
